                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        <a href="/school-policy-notices" class="text-red text-decoration-underline">
                            School Policy Notices
                        </a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="school_resource">
                    <p class="fs-18 ff-bb">Athletics, Clubs & Activities</p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        <a href="/kids-club" class="text-red text-decoration-underline">
