                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        <a href="https://montessori.wlps.net/" target="_blank" class="text-red text-decoration-underline">
                            EduCare Before/After Care & No School/Snow Day Care
                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        <a href="https://sideline.bsnsports.com/schools/michigan/whitmorelake/whitmore-lake-high-school" target="_blank" class="text-red text-decoration-underline">
                            WL Athletics Spiritwear
                        </a>
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
